<html
  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
  xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
  xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
  xmlns:i18n="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/i18n"
  xml:lang="en"
  lang="en"
  dir="ltr"
  metal:use-macro="view/macro:page/main_only"
  i18n:domain="launchpad">
  <body>
    <tal:heading metal:fill-slot="heading">
      <h1>Translation groups</h1>
    </tal:heading>
    <div metal:fill-slot="main"
         style="max-width:800px; margin-bottom: 2em;">
      <p>
        A <dfn>translation group</dfn> is a set of teams or individual
        supervisors chosen by the owner of a distribution, project group, or
        project to manage its translations.
        Each team or supervisor in a group is responsible for one or more
        specific languages.
      </p>

      <p>
        To read more about translation groups, you can go through our
        <a href="
            https://help.launchpad.net/Translations/JoiningATranslationGroup">
          documentation</a>.
      </p>

      <p>
        If you are trying to decide which translation group to use for your
        project, we recommend
        <a href="launchpad-translators">Launchpad Translators</a> â€” read
        more about
        <a href="https://help.launchpad.net/Translations/LaunchpadTranslators">
          what that group is about</a>.
      </p>

      <table class="listing" id="translation-groups" width="100%"
             style="margin-top:1em; margin-bottom:1em;">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th style="text-align:left;">Translation Group</th>
            <th>Supervises Translations for</th>
            <th>Created</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr tal:repeat="group context">
            <td>
              <a
                tal:content="group/title/fmt:shorten/57"
                tal:attributes="href group/name"
              >Ubuntu Translators</a>
            </td>
            <td>
              <tal:projects condition="group/top_projects">
                <span tal:repeat="project group/top_projects">
                  <a tal:replace="structure project/fmt:link">ubuntu
                  </a><tal:comma condition="not: repeat/project/end">, 
                  </tal:comma>
                </span>
                <span tal:condition="group/number_of_remaining_projects">
                  and
                  <a tal:attributes="href group/name"
                     tal:content="
                         string:${group/number_of_remaining_projects} other">
                    5 other</a>
                  projects</span>
              </tal:projects>
            </td>
            <td>
              <span class="sortkey"
                tal:content="group/datecreated/fmt:datetime" />
              <span
                tal:attributes="title group/datecreated/fmt:datetime"
                tal:content="group/datecreated/fmt:approximatedate">
                2007-08-15
              </span>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
      <tal:can-edit condition="context/required:launchpad.Admin">
        <span class="add sprite" style="float:right;">
          <a href="+new">Create a new translation group</a>
        </span>
      </tal:can-edit>
    </div><!--main-->
  </body>
</html>
